{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Derailed</strong> - a first-person psychological horror game in the &quot;walking simulator&quot; genre.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Average playtime: 60 minutes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/extras/Corridor.gif?t=1735931409\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Raindrops crash against the leaky roof, with a damp scent lingering in the air. Decades-worn walls, rattling window panes in the wind, and the hollow echo of footsteps \u2014 all around, the setting seems to repeatedly warn you that you don\u2019t belong here. But there is no other choice; the only path is forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/extras/Electric.gif?t=1735931409\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Game Features:</i></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Walking simulator&quot; genre;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with objects and solve puzzles to progress through the story;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover the secret hidden within an almost-forgotten depot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in a haunting environment with detailed locations;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rich 3D sound that fully envelops you in the atmosphere;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Short playtime, allowing you to complete the game in one evening and maintain suspense until the very end.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>email: <a href=\"mailto:deformeddreams@gmail.com\">deformeddreams@gmail.com</a></i></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735931409","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240310/page_bg_generated.jp